* Xte 
  xautomation generate fake inputs to x window.

* lm-sensors

  sensors detect provided

* i8kfan and .mon

* change language

  locale -a lists all the language available for use by system and apps.

  /etc/locale.gen file has list of languge supports.

  Uncomment any and all language you wanna use.

  and run locale-gen to generate and add language to .conf


  and finally to change system language run

  localectl set-locale LANG=en_US.utf8

* date and time got resetted?

  run the following commmand if you're online to get the time update

  timedatectl set-ntp true

* wanna find properties os x window?

  xprop :)

  


